WEBVTT

00:01.040 --> 00:02.255
<i>Previously on</i> The Resident...

00:02.291 --> 00:05.058
I'm Dr. AJ Austin in the flesh.

00:05.094 --> 00:06.927
<i>One of the most gifted
cardiothoracic surgeons</i>

00:06.963 --> 00:08.328
<i>is meeting with me today.</i>

00:08.364 --> 00:09.763
I still plan to cut.

00:09.799 --> 00:11.331
Why bother?

00:11.367 --> 00:12.967
Keep Austin away
from conscious patients.

00:13.003 --> 00:14.802
York, what did you shove
up your rectum this time?

00:14.838 --> 00:16.068
<i>It was the first time that...</i>

00:16.105 --> 00:17.938
That you had extracted

00:17.974 --> 00:21.441
an object from the colon
of an adult male?

00:21.477 --> 00:24.078
- Yes.
- <i>I like working for Hunter.</i>

00:24.114 --> 00:26.779
She likes everyone who works
for her to be discreet.

00:26.815 --> 00:28.448
Sorry, I didn't mean
to startle you.

00:28.484 --> 00:29.984
<i>I'm just delivering
your groceries.</i>

00:30.020 --> 00:32.152
<i>I think someone's following me.</i>

00:32.188 --> 00:34.357
I'm just starting to realize
how far Lane's willing to go.

